OL,6,FLabour has called for Tata Steel to
OL,7,Fmake "no irreversible decisions" to be
OL,8,Fprior to the General Election next
OL,9,Fmonth.
OL,11,FFirst Minister met with management and
OL,12,Ftrade unions in Port Talbot today in
OL,13,Fan effort to keep iron and steelmaking
OL,14,Fgoing at the site.
OL,16,F"We're interested in winning an
OL,17,Fargument for the future, the future of
OL,18,Fthis workforce, but more than that,
OL,19,Fthe future of our industrial base, and
OL,20,Ffuture in Wales and Britain," Mr
OL,21,FGething said.
