OL,6,FSeveral factors are said to have led
OL,7,Fto the company's decision, with
OL,8,Ffinancial losses amounting to #1
OL,9,Fmillion a day a key factor, according
OL,10,Fto Tata Steel.
OL,12,FUnions are opposed to the plans to
OL,13,Fclose both blast furnaces this year
OL,14,Fbefore switching to a greener form of
OL,15,Fproduction which needs fewer workers.
