OL,6,FJo Stevens said today that she was
OL,7,F"convinced" that progress could be
OL,8,Fmade and called for Tata Steel not to
OL,9,Fswitch off the blast furnaces.
OL,11,F"We want them to look at the union
OL,12,Fplan again, we want to talk to them,
