OL,6,FAt the moment, one blast furnace is
OL,7,Fset to close by the end of June and
OL,8,Fthe other by the end of September.
OL,10,FSpeaking on behalf of the Community
OL,11,FUnion, Roy Rickhuss thanked the Labour
OL,12,Fparty for "stepping up" to the
OL,13,Fchallenges the steel industry face.
OL,15,F"Labour's pledge of #3 billion for our
OL,16,Fsteel industry and Johnny Reynolds'
OL,17,Fmeeting with our members today
OL,18,Fdemonstrates that Labour has a bold
OL,19,Fvision for our steel industry, one
OL,20,Fthat will place the UK economy and
OL,21,Fworkers at its heart."
